spec_data.Name: perl-Net-Google-AuthSub
spec_data.Description:
AuthSub is Google's method of authentication for their web
services. It is also used by other web sites.

You can read more about it here.
    http://code.google.com/apis/accounts/Authentication.html

A Google Group for AuthSub is here.
    http://groups.google.com/group/Google-Accounts-API
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 02:16:58 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Provides interface to interact with sites that implement Google style AuthSub
